{"title":"士兵的歌","authors":["于书恒"],"dates":[{"year":1997,"month":8,"day":5}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"士兵的歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于书恒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"边防哨所"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个战士说，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他是墙上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拧着中国地图的那颗钉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不能挪位，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不能松动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看住风刮虫咬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"守着四边完整。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"边防哨所，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钉的位置，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钉的使命。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士与少年"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大雨天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士搀着老大娘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走进了小学生的课本。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小学生乐了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"认出战士是雷锋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"缠着不让离开，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没完没了地讲故事，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一直把小学生都讲成雷锋……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新兵的家信"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"信中说："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我为母亲扛起枪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我为母亲守边疆。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"母亲怪儿：傻孩子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当兵不能光为娘。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爹说，那是诗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"母亲是黄河，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"母亲是长江，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"军队出息人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"儿子在成长……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（作者单位：山东烟台日报社）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}